Question:
Find the Last Word length of a given sentence.

Program:
class Solution {
    public int lengthOfLastWord(String s) {
        String[] s1=s.split(" ");
        return s1[s1.length-1].length();
        
    }
}

Time Complexity:O(1)
Space Complexity:O(n)

Input: s = "Hello World"
Output: 5
Explanation: The last word is "World" with length 5.
